          <span class="text-[10px] px-2 py-1 rounded-full" style="background:rgba(212,181,199,0.15);color:var(--text-soft)">🌱 自我成长</span>
          <span class="text-[10px] px-2 py-1 rounded-full" style="background:rgba(212,181,199,0.15);color:var(--text-soft)">🧭 人生方向</span>
          <span class="text-[10px] px-2 py-1 rounded-full" style="background:rgba(212,181,199,0.15);color:var(--text-soft)">🏥 健康显化</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="glass-card p-5 text-center">
      <div class="text-sm font-medium mb-2" style="color:var(--theme-text)">💡 首次体验</div>
      <div class="text-2xl font-bold mb-1" style="color:#F59E0B">¥99</div>
      <div class="text-xs mb-4" style="color:var(--text-mute)">30分钟诊断 · 原价 ¥199</div>
      <button onclick="showToast('预约系统即将开放，敬请期待 ✨')" class="btn-primary w-full py-3 rounded-xl">立即预约</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ========== 隐私政策与用户协议 ========== -->
<section id="page-privacy" class="page" style="padding-bottom:100px;">
  <div class="glass-header sticky top-0 z-40 px-5 py-4">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between max-w-lg mx-auto">
      <button onclick="goHome()" class="soft-btn w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.6)">
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M19 12H5M12 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
      </button>
      <h1 class="text-lg font-medium" style="color:var(--theme-text)">隐私与协议</h1>
      <div class="w-10"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto px-5 py-6">
    <div class="glass-card p-5 mb-4">
      <h3 class="font-medium mb-3">🔒 隐私政策</h3>
      <div class="space-y-3 text-xs" style="color:var(--text-soft)">
        <p><span class="font-medium" style="color:var(--theme-text)">1. 数据存储</span><br>所有数据仅存储在您的设备本地（localStorage），我们不会上传任何个人信息到服务器。</p>
        <p><span class="font-medium" style="color:var(--theme-text)">2. 数据导出</span><br>您可以随时导出全部数据为JSON文件，实现跨设备迁移。</p>
        <p><span class="font-medium" style="color:var(--theme-text)">3. 第三方服务</span><br>本应用使用浏览器内置语音合成API（Web Speech），音频数据仅在本地处理。</p>
        <p><span class="font-medium" style="color:var(--theme-text)">4. 删除数据</span><br>清除浏览器缓存或卸载应用即可删除所有数据。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="glass-card p-5 mb-4">
      <h3 class="font-medium mb-3">📜 用户协议</h3>
      <div class="space-y-3 text-xs" style="color:var(--text-soft)">
        <p><span class="font-medium" style="color:var(--theme-text)">1. 免责声明</span><br>本应用提供的显化方法、肯定语等内容仅供自我探索与心理辅助，不构成医疗、心理或法律建议。</p>
        <p><span class="font-medium" style="color:var(--theme-text)">2. 心理健康</span><br>如有严重心理问题，请及时寻求专业心理咨询师或医疗机构的帮助。</p>
        <p><span class="font-medium" style="color:var(--theme-text)">3. 付费说明</span><br>当前所有付费功能为演示状态，实际扣费需通过正式支付渠道完成。</p>
        <p><span class="font-medium" style="color:var(--theme-text)">4. 知识产权</span><br>应用内所有原创内容版权归星愿花园所有。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-xs text-center" style="color:var(--text-mute)">最后更新：2025年7月</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ========== 反馈与帮助弹窗 ========== -->
<div id="feedback-modal" class="modal-backdrop" onclick="if(event.target===this)closeFeedbackModal()">
  <div class="modal-content p-6 text-center" style="max-width:360px">
    <div class="text-4xl mb-3">💌</div>
    <h3 class="font-medium text-lg mb-2" style="font-family:'ZCOOL XiaoWei',sans-serif">你的声音很重要</h3>
    <p class="text-sm mb-4" style="color:var(--text-soft)">遇到bug？有新想法？告诉我们</p>
    <textarea id="feedback-text" class="dream-input mb-3" rows="4" placeholder="描述你的问题或建议..."></textarea>
    <select id="feedback-type" class="dream-input mb-3">
      <option value="bug">🐛 功能异常</option>
      <option value="feature">✨ 新功能建议</option>
      <option value="content">📖 内容建议</option>
      <option value="other">💭 其他</option>
    </select>
    <button onclick="submitFeedback()" class="btn-primary w-full py-3 rounded-xl mb-2">提交反馈</button>
    <button onclick="closeFeedbackModal()" class="text-xs" style="color:var(--text-mute)">稍后再说</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ========== 静心呼吸器 ========== -->
<section id="page-breathe" class="page" style="padding-bottom:100px;">
  <div class="glass-header sticky top-0 z-40 px-5 py-4">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between max-w-lg mx-auto">
      <button onclick="goHome()" class="soft-btn w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.6)">
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M19 12H5M12 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
      </button>
      <h1 class="text-lg font-medium" style="color:var(--theme-text)">静心呼吸</h1>
      <div class="w-10"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto px-5 py-6">
    <div class="glass-card p-5 mb-6 text-center">
      <div class="text-3xl mb-2">🌬️</div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-medium mb-1" style="font-family:'ZCOOL XiaoWei',sans-serif">用呼吸回归当下</h2>
      <p class="text-sm" style="color:var(--text-soft)">每一次呼吸，都是一次显化的校准</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 呼吸模式选择 -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 mb-6">
      <div id="breathe-mode-calm" class="glass-card p-3 text-center cursor-pointer card-hover" style="border:2px solid var(--theme-text)" onclick="selectBreatheMode('calm',this)">
        <div class="text-2xl mb-1">🧘</div>
        <div class="text-xs font-medium" style="color:var(--theme-text)">4-7-8 放松</div>
        <div class="text-[10px]" style="color:var(--text-mute)">减压助眠</div>
      </div>
      <div id="breathe-mode-box" class="glass-card p-3 text-center cursor-pointer card-hover" onclick="selectBreatheMode('box',this)">
        <div class="text-2xl mb-1">📦</div>
        <div class="text-xs font-medium" style="color:var(--theme-text)">Box 专注</div>
        <div class="text-[10px]" style="color:var(--text-mute)">平衡能量</div>
      </div>
      <div id="breathe-mode-coherent" class="glass-card p-3 text-center cursor-pointer card-hover" onclick="selectBreatheMode('coherent',this)">
        <div class="text-2xl mb-1">💫</div>
        <div class="text-xs font-medium" style="color:var(--theme-text)">Coherent 心流</div>
        <div class="text-[10px]" style="color:var(--text-mute)">情绪稳定</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 呼吸动画区域 -->
    <div class="glass-card p-8 mb-6 text-center relative overflow-hidden" style="min-height:320px">
      <div id="breathe-circle" class="mx-auto rounded-full flex items-center justify-center relative" style="width:180px;height:180px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(212,181,199,0.3),rgba(184,169,201,0.2));border:2px solid rgba(212,181,199,0.4);transition:transform 0.1s linear">
        <div id="breathe-text" class="text-lg font-medium" style="color:var(--theme-text);font-family:'ZCOOL XiaoWei',sans-serif">吸气</div>
        <div id="breathe-timer" class="absolute text-2xl font-bold" style="color:var(--theme-text);opacity:0.3;bottom:20px">4</div>
      </div>
      <div id="breathe-instruction" class="mt-6 text-sm" style="color:var(--text-soft)">鼻子吸气4秒 → 屏息7秒 → 嘴巴呼气8秒</div>
      <div id="breathe-progress" class="mt-4 w-full h-1 rounded-full" style="background:rgba(212,181,199,0.15)"><div id="breathe-bar" class="h-full rounded-full" style="width:0%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#D4B5C7,#B8A9C9);transition:width 0.3s"></div></div>
      <div id="breathe-round" class="mt-3 text-xs" style="color:var(--text-mute)">第 0 / 10 轮</div>
    </div>

    <!-- 呼吸音设置 -->
    <div class="glass-card p-4 mb-6">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-medium mb-3" style="color:var(--theme-text)">🎵 呼吸音</h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-3">
        <div>
          <div class="text-xs mb-1" style="color:var(--text-mute)">呼吸引导</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <button id="breathe-tone-btn" onclick="toggleBreatheTone()" class="flex-1 py-2 rounded-lg text-xs font-medium" style="background:rgba(212,181,199,0.15);color:var(--theme-text)">🔕 关闭</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-xs mb-1" style="color:var(--text-mute)">背景环境音</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <button id="breathe-ambient-btn" onclick="toggleBreatheAmbient()" class="flex-1 py-2 rounded-lg text-xs font-medium" style="background:rgba(212,181,199,0.15);color:var(--theme-text)">🔕 关闭</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="breathe-ambient-options" class="hidden">
        <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
          <button onclick="setBreatheAmbient('white')" class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs" style="background:rgba(212,181,199,0.1);color:var(--text-soft)">🌊 白噪音</button>
          <button onclick="setBreatheAmbient('pink')" class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs" style="background:rgba(212,181,199,0.1);color:var(--text-soft)">🌸 粉红噪声</button>
          <button onclick="setBreatheAmbient('ocean')" class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs" style="background:rgba(212,181,199,0.1);color:var(--text-soft)">🌊 海浪</button>
          <button onclick="setBreatheAmbient('rain')" class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs" style="background:rgba(212,181,199,0.1);color:var(--text-soft)">🌧️ 雨声</button>
          <button onclick="setBreatheAmbient('forest')" class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs" style="background:rgba(212,181,199,0.1);color:var(--text-soft)">🌲 森林</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 控制按钮 -->
    <div class="flex gap-3 justify-center">
      <button id="breathe-start-btn" onclick="startBreathe()" class="btn-primary px-8 py-3 rounded-xl text-sm">开始练习</button>
      <button id="breathe-stop-btn" onclick="stopBreathe()" class="btn-soft px-8 py-3 rounded-xl text-sm hidden">结束</button>
    </div>

    <!-- 练习记录 -->
    <div class="glass-card p-4 mt-6">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-medium mb-3" style="color:var(--theme-text)">📊 今日练习</h3>
      <div id="breathe-stats" class="text-sm" style="color:var(--text-soft)">今日完成 0 轮静心呼吸</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ========== 语音肯定语录制 ========== -->
<section id="page-voice" class="page" style="padding-bottom:100px;">
  <div class="glass-header sticky top-0 z-40 px-5 py-4">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between max-w-lg mx-auto">
      <button onclick="goHome()" class="soft-btn w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.6)">
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M19 12H5M12 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
      </button>
      <h1 class="text-lg font-medium" style="color:var(--theme-text)">我的声音</h1>
      <div class="w-10"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto px-5 py-6">
    <div class="glass-card p-5 mb-6 text-center">
      <div class="text-3xl mb-2">🎙️</div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-medium mb-1" style="font-family:'ZCOOL XiaoWei',sans-serif">听自己说肯定语</h2>
      <p class="text-sm" style="color:var(--text-soft)">潜意识对自己声音的接受度最高</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 录音区域 -->
    <div class="glass-card p-6 mb-6 text-center">
      <div id="voice-record-btn" onclick="toggleVoiceRecord()" class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl cursor-pointer mb-4" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#D4B5C7,#B8A9C9);color:white;box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(212,181,199,0.3)">
        🎙️
      </div>
      <div id="voice-status" class="text-sm font-medium mb-2" style="color:var(--theme-text)">点击录制你的肯定语</div>
      <div id="voice-timer" class="text-xs" style="color:var(--text-mute)">00:00</div>

      <!-- 录音波形动画 -->
      <div id="voice-wave" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-1 mt-4 h-8 opacity-0">
        <div class="w-1 rounded-full" style="height:16px;background:#D4B5C7;animation:voiceWave 0.5s ease-in-out infinite"></div>
        <div class="w-1 rounded-full" style="height:24px;background:#D4B5C7;animation:voiceWave 0.6s ease-in-out infinite 0.1s"></div>
        <div class="w-1 rounded-full" style="height:20px;background:#D4B5C7;animation:voiceWave 0.4s ease-in-out infinite 0.2s"></div>
        <div class="w-1 rounded-full" style="height:28px;background:#D4B5C7;animation:voiceWave 0.7s ease-in-out infinite 0.05s"></div>
        <div class="w-1 rounded-full" style="height:18px;background:#D4B5C7;animation:voiceWave 0.5s ease-in-out infinite 0.15s"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 已录制的肯定语列表 -->
    <div id="voice-recordings-list" class="space-y-3 mb-6"></div>

    <!-- 推荐肯定语 -->
    <div class="glass-card p-4">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-medium mb-3" style="color:var(--theme-text)">💡 推荐录制</h3>
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <div class="text-sm p-2 rounded-lg cursor-pointer" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);color:var(--text-soft)" onclick="fillVoiceInput('我已经拥有我想要的一切')">我已经拥有我想要的一切</div>
        <div class="text-sm p-2 rounded-lg cursor-pointer" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);color:var(--text-soft)" onclick="fillVoiceInput('我值得被爱，被珍惜，被尊重')">我值得被爱，被珍惜，被尊重</div>
        <div class="text-sm p-2 rounded-lg cursor-pointer" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);color:var(--text-soft)" onclick="fillVoiceInput('我的SP正在向我走来，我们的关系完美和谐')">我的SP正在向我走来，我们的关系完美和谐</div>
        <div class="text-sm p-2 rounded-lg cursor-pointer" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);color:var(--text-soft)" onclick="fillVoiceInput('金钱轻松而丰盛地流向我')">金钱轻松而丰盛地流向我</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

